div.h1: Fault Cascade: Triple Fault Cause Chain

p.strong: "When the exception handler becomes the exception"

div.p: SS (if CPL change) ESP (if CPL change) EFLAGS CS EIP Error Code (optional)

g.title: IDT gate points to unmapped memory or ring 0 code with DPL=0
TSS.ESP0 is garbage or TSS segment selector invalid
TSS.ESP0 not updated on context switch

Page tables don't map IDT address
